Washed-up ballplayer say what?

20:04.820 --> 20:07.770
l got an agent and
a record producer coming, all right?

20:07.860 --> 20:10.370
You want that ball, you better
make me look good, all right?

20:10.460 --> 20:13.770
A Justin Timberlake mask
couldn't make you look good.

20:13.860 --> 20:15.490
-Do you know who l am?
-Yeah.

20:15.580 --> 20:17.690
You're the guy l used to look up to.

20:17.780 --> 20:20.690
