Jackson, hold on. Wait.

20:37.940 --> 20:39.530
l don't understand.

20:39.620 --> 20:43.320
l didn't let you off the hook.
l wanted you to suffer.

20:43.420 --> 20:47.250
l saw that last number.
l think we've both suffered enough.

20:47.340 --> 20:50.170
-So you don't want your ball any more?
-Nah.

20:50.260 --> 20:52.330
No autograph is worth this.

20:53.020 --> 20:54.210
Thanks.

20:55.300 --> 20:57.490
Hold on! l forgot something.

20:57.580 --> 20:58.640
Hey!

20:59.660 --> 21:00.850
-Hey, Joey.
-Yeah.

21:00.940 --> 21:03.010
-Ready for the big finale?
-What finale?

21:03.100 --> 21:04.240
Yours.

21:04.860 --> 21:06.570
One meatball to go!

21:12.700 --> 21:14.530
Right in the cannolis.

21:18.060 --> 21:21.130
You know, it was awful nice of you
to forgive Mr vitolo.

21:21.220 --> 21:25.970
