the baseball and he apologised,

21:26.060 --> 21:29.410
l figured it was time for me
to let him off the hook.

21:31.820 --> 21:35.730
Now, if you'll excuse me.
l promised Joey one last song.

21:36.300 --> 21:37.810
Hit it, Paulie!

22:01.540 --> 22:05.370
